public class DynamicEntity
extends com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.common.entity.Entity
implements com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.common.interfaces.IDynamicEntity

DynamicEntity extends Entity and implements IDynamicEntity to represent an actual dynamic entity in the game world.

DynamicEntity does not provide a default constructor for binary import and export. This prevents any attempts of exporting DynamicEntity into a binary format.
